description:
Update column editor args for autocomplete to accept a function that returns the options.  When filtering the items, if this function is set, then we call it and use the returned value as the options to display.  If not set, it works as previously designed.  This should pass down to the autocomplete, and the autocomplete handles the callback.

Depends on: #2710 

